I am not going to lie.  I rarely seed shit after I get done downloading it.  If I try to upload more than about 15 kbs while downloading, my DL speed goes to shit.  And honestly, I have a 2 Mbit upload, which means, maxed out, I am only sending out about 220 kbps....... If i had a blazing fast upload, I would seed.

The biggest thing for me is uploading SLOWS down my wireless network.  I use a PS3 with netflix and many other computers on my wireless.  If uploading didn't slow my down speed, I would seed all day, even at a slow 2mbit.  

And  LOL @ people bitching about getting 700 kbs down.  What... you whinning that you maybe have to wait 30-45 min for your download.  Fuck, I barely get 700 kbs on a single torrent ever, and I have 20 Mbit down..... I NEVER see over 1.5 mbs

I just would like to add.  Are we seriously getting to a point in society where people are actually bitching and whinning about having to wait an hour for a HIGH DEFINITION download to finish....

Oh by the way, we are STEALING this.  Next time you come on TPB to bitch in ANY torrent thread, remember... WE ARE STEALING.  THIS IS FREE.  As in, because of EZTV and TPB and MANY OTHERS, I do NOT have to pay 50 bucks a month for cable television!
